sentences: Charlie Green (born 16 February 1997) is an English-Filipino singer from Droitwich, Worcestershire, England.
Green is best known for appearing on the second series of Britain's Got Talent in 2008.
In February 2010, Green signed a two-year recording contract and agency with Viva Records.
Green was born on 16 February 1997 in Droitwich, Worcestershire to Roger Green who is English and Cecilia Sumargo who is a Filipina.
